    <h1>Privacy Policy (English)</h1>
    <p>...Privacy Policy
​This application collects some Personal Data from its Users.
​Types of Data collected: The app saves workout data (levels, selected exercises, history) locally on the user's device. It also uses advertising identifiers through Google AdMob.
​Processing method: Workout data stays exclusively on the user's device. Advertising data is managed by Google according to its policy.
​Purpose: Data is used for the app's functionality and to display advertisements.
​User Rights: Users can delete all workout data at any time using the "Reset" button in the app settings.
​Contact: mastriamarco@gmail.com...</p>
